<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨٠ سورة عبس]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٧]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّى <span class="c2">(١)</span> أَنْ جاءَهُ الْأَعْمى <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَما يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُ يَزَّكَّى <span class="c2">(٣)</span> أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنْفَعَهُ الذِّكْرى <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَمَّا مَنِ اسْتَغْنى <span class="c2">(٥)</span> فَأَنْتَ لَهُ تَصَدَّى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَما عَلَيْكَ أَلاَّ يَزَّكَّى <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَبَسَ تغير وجهه كارها.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَتَوَلَّى وأعرض.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>والضمير فيهما للنبى صلى الله عليه وسلم.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> أَنْ جاءَهُ الْأَعْمى:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَنْ جاءَهُ الْأَعْمى لأن جاءه الأعمى يسأله عن أمر دينه.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> وَما يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُ يَزَّكَّى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَعَلَّهُ لعل هذا الأعمى.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَزَّكَّى يتطهر بما يتلقاه عنك.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنْفَعَهُ الذِّكْرى:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ أو يتعظ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>الذِّكْرى العظة.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> أَمَّا مَنِ اسْتَغْنى:</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>اسْتَغْنى بثروته وقوته.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> فَأَنْتَ لَهُ تَصَدَّى:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>تَصَدَّى تقبل عليه وتهتم بتبليغه دعوتك.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> وَما عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّى:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَما عَلَيْكَ وأي شىء عليك.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>أَلَّا يَزَّكَّى إذا لم يتطهر بالإيمان.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>